        "TileImage": "$($repository 63c92e76-14c9-471c-a8fe-b25567661a3c).Image",
        "Description": "Do you know what is like to get a bad steak, 47?\r\rWell, the people on Ambrose are used to it. The chefs on the island just don&apos;t care about taste and hygiene. They use the same kithen knifes and meat forks every day without washing them.\r\rMake them retire, 47",
